        "description": {
            "value": "<p>As a member of dragonkind, you project unflappable confidence (that collapses catastrophically against the deadliest foes).</p>\n<p>When you roll a success on a saving throw against a fear effect, you get a critical success instead. When you roll a failure against a fear effect, you get a critical failure instead.</p>\n<p>In addition, when you attempt to @Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.Demoralize]{Demoralize} a foe of your level or lower, you gain a +1 circumstance bonus to the Intimidation check.</p>"
        },
